         <abstract id="aspace_103fd7f2597f743b673e0c245e6c0e78">Chiefly fragments of manuscripts from Warren Ives Bradley's published books. Also included is a scrapbook of reviews, household expense lists and photographs of Bradley and his brother, Oliver Burritt Bradley.</abstract>
